<element x="12" y="78" anchor="0" width="300" height="164" id="Wheel" visible="0" alpha="1" angle="0" scalex="1" scaley="1" center="4" handcursor="0" hotspotproxy="Wheel" type="text" text="&lt;b&gt;Wheel Room&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;In this area, deep inside the ship&#39;s hull, you can see a part of the mechanism used to steer the ship.&lt;p&gt;&lt;b&gt;Stafell y llyw&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;Yn yr ardal hyn, yn ddwfn yng nghorff y llong, gallwch weld rhan o&#8217;r fecanwaith a ddefnyddiwyd i lywio&#8217;r llong.&lt;/p&gt;" align="0" color="0x000000" bordercolor="0x484848" borderalpha="1" backgroundcolor="0xffffff" backgroundalpha="1" backgroundvisible="1" borderwidth="1" borderradius="19" wordwrap="1" scrollbar="0" autosize="1" >
<action src="click" type="tooglevisible" value="" value2="" target="$self" />
</element>
<element x="12" y="78" anchor="0" width="300" height="164" id="Food" visible="0" alpha="1" angle="0" scalex="1" scaley="1" center="4" handcursor="0" hotspotproxy="Food" type="text" text="&lt;b&gt;Food at Sea&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;Food was divided in to &quot;wet&quot; and &quot;dry&quot; provisions. Wet provisions included salt beef, pork, suet (beef fat), lime juice and rum. Dry provisions included things like biscuits, beans, peas, flour, rice, sugar, preserved meat and chocolate. Food was carefully stored in casks and drums in holds deep in the ship, making sure the older provisions were on top so everything would be used up in order of freshness. &lt;p&gt;&lt;b&gt;Bwyd ar y m&#244;r&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;Rhannwyd bwyd mewn i ddarpariaeth &#8216;gwlyb&#8217; a &#8216;sych&#8217;. Roedd darpariaeth gwlyb yn cynnwys cig eidion wedi ei halltu, porc, suet, sudd leim a rym. Roedd darpariaeth sych yn cynnwys bwydydd fel bisgedi, ffa, pys, blawd, reis, siwgr, cig cadw a siocled. Storiwyd y bwyd yn ofalus mewn casgenni a drymiau mewn howldiau yn ddwfn yng nghrombil y llong, gan sicrhau fod y bwydydd hynaf ar ben fel bod popeth yn cael eu defnyddio yn nhrefn eu ffresni.&lt;/p&gt;" align="0" color="0x000000" bordercolor="0x484848" borderalpha="1" backgroundcolor="0xffffff" backgroundalpha="1" backgroundvisible="1" borderwidth="1" borderradius="19" wordwrap="1" scrollbar="0" autosize="1" >
<action src="click" type="tooglevisible" value="" value2="" target="$self" />
</element>
<element x="12" y="78" anchor="0" width="300" height="164" id="Galley" visible="0" alpha="1" angle="0" scalex="1" scaley="1" center="4" handcursor="0" hotspotproxy="Galley" type="text" text="&lt;b&gt;Galley&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;This is the ship&#39;s galley (kitchen) aboard the World War One warship, HMS Caroline. From this small space over 300 sailors would have been fed.&lt;p&gt;&lt;b&gt;Cegin&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;Dyma cegin y llong ar long rhyfel y Rhyfel Byd Cyntaf, HMS Caroline. O&#8217;r stafell fach hon byddai dros 300 o forwyr wedi cael eu bwydo.&lt;/p&gt;" align="0" color="0x000000" bordercolor="0x484848" borderalpha="1" backgroundcolor="0xffffff" backgroundalpha="1" backgroundvisible="1" borderwidth="1" borderradius="19" wordwrap="1" scrollbar="0" autosize="1" >
<action src="click" type="tooglevisible" value="" value2="" target="$self" />
</element>
<element x="12" y="78" anchor="0" width="300" height="164" id="Telegraph" visible="0" alpha="1" angle="0" scalex="1" scaley="1" center="4" handcursor="0" hotspotproxy="Telegraph" type="text" text="&lt;b&gt;Telegraph&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;This telegraph allows the officers to send messages from the ship&#39;s bridge down to the crew in the tiller room to instruct them to adjust the ship&#39;s course. &lt;p&gt;&lt;b&gt;Telegraff&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;Roedd y telegraff hwn yn caniat&#225;u i swyddogion hala negeseuon o bont y llong lawr i&#8217;r criw yn stafell y llyw gyda chyfarwyddiadau am gwrs y llong.&lt;/p&gt;" align="0" color="0x000000" bordercolor="0x484848" borderalpha="1" backgroundcolor="0xffffff" backgroundalpha="1" backgroundvisible="1" borderwidth="1" borderradius="19" wordwrap="1" scrollbar="0" autosize="1" >
<action src="click" type="tooglevisible" value="" value2="" target="$self" />
</element>
<element x="12" y="78" anchor="0" width="300" height="164" id="Corridor" visible="0" alpha="1" angle="0" scalex="1" scaley="1" center="4" handcursor="0" hotspotproxy="Corridor" type="text" text="&lt;b&gt;Corridor&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;Here you can see how sailors moved around the ship. Narrow corridors connected cabins and spaces together and metal ladders led down to other decks and storage areas. The water-tight hatches would be closed in an emergency. &lt;p&gt;&lt;b&gt;Coridor&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;Yma gallwch weld sut byddai morwyr wedi symud o gwmpas y llong. Roedd coridorau cul yn cysylltu cabanau a stafelloedd gyda&#8217;i gilydd ac roedd ysgolion metel yn arwain lawr i ddeciau eraill a mannau&#8217;r storfeydd. Byddai&#8217;r hatshus dwrglos yn cael eu cau mewn argyfwng.&lt;/p&gt;" align="0" color="0x000000" bordercolor="0x484848" borderalpha="1" backgroundcolor="0xffffff" backgroundalpha="1" backgroundvisible="1" borderwidth="1" borderradius="19" wordwrap="1" scrollbar="0" autosize="1" >
<action src="click" type="tooglevisible" value="" value2="" target="$self" />
</element>
<element x="12" y="78" anchor="0" width="300" height="164" id="LivingQuarters" visible="0" alpha="1" angle="0" scalex="1" scaley="1" center="4" handcursor="0" hotspotproxy="LivingQuarters" type="text" text="&lt;b&gt;Living quarters on a ship&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt; Most sailors on a ship would sleep in hammocks hung from metal rings in the ceiling. Officers slept separately but most still in hammocks. Only the captain and the highest ranking officers had cabins of their own.&lt;p&gt;&lt;b&gt;Stafelloedd byw ar long&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;Byddai&#8217;r rhan fwyaf o forwyr ar long wedi cysgu mewn gwely crog a fyddai wedi cael eu hongian o&#8217;r nenfwd. Roedd swyddogion yn cysgu ar wah&#226;n ond y rhan fwyaf o hyd mewn gwelyau crog. Dim ond y capten a&#8217;r swyddogion uwch fyddai wedi berchen ar gabanau eu hunain.&lt;/p&gt;" align="0" color="0x000000" bordercolor="0x484848" borderalpha="1" backgroundcolor="0xffffff" backgroundalpha="1" backgroundvisible="1" borderwidth="1" borderradius="19" wordwrap="1" scrollbar="0" autosize="1" >
