<element x="12" y="78" anchor="0" width="300" height="164" id="Compass" visible="0" alpha="1" angle="0" scalex="1" scaley="1" center="4" handcursor="0" hotspotproxy="Compass" type="text" text="&lt;b&gt;Compass&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;The ship&#39;s compass showed the crew which direction they were heading in and they used it to guide the ship on the correct course. &lt;p&gt;&lt;b&gt;Cwmpawd&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;Roedd cwmpawd y llong yn dangos i&#8217;r criw i ba gyfeiriad roeddent yn mynd a defnyddiwyd hi i dywys y llong ar y trywydd cywir.&lt;/p&gt;" align="0" color="0x000000" bordercolor="0x484848" borderalpha="1" backgroundcolor="0xffffff" backgroundalpha="1" backgroundvisible="1" borderwidth="1" borderradius="19" wordwrap="1" scrollbar="0" autosize="1" >
