<element x="12" y="78" anchor="0" width="300" height="164" id="Guns" visible="0" alpha="1" angle="0" scalex="1" scaley="1" center="4" handcursor="0" hotspotproxy="Guns" type="text" text="&lt;b&gt;HMS Caroline&#39;s guns&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;HMS Caroline&#39;s main armament was a pair of six inch guns. These guns had a range of over 19,000 metres - over 11 miles.  Larger battleships were armed with guns that could fire at a range of nearly 20 miles.&lt;p&gt;&lt;b&gt;Magnelau HMS Caroline&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;Prif arf HMS Caroline oedd p&#226;r o fagnelau chwe modfedd. Roedd gan y magnelau yma bellter o dros 19,000 o fetrau &#8211; dros 11 milltir. Arfogwyd cadlongau mwy gan fagnelau oedd yn gallu tanio hyd at 20 milltir.&lt;/p&gt;" align="0" color="0x000000" bordercolor="0x484848" borderalpha="1" backgroundcolor="0xffffff" backgroundalpha="1" backgroundvisible="1" borderwidth="1" borderradius="19" wordwrap="1" scrollbar="0" autosize="1" >
