<element x="12" y="78" anchor="0" width="300" height="164" id="Torpedoes" visible="0" alpha="1" angle="0" scalex="1" scaley="1" center="4" handcursor="0" hotspotproxy="Torpedoes" type="text" text="&lt;b&gt;Torpedoes&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;HMS Caroline was also armed with torpedoes. Torpedoes are underwater explosives. They are launched out of torpedo tubes and move through the water under their own power. By hitting their target below the water line, torpedoes can cause catastrophic damage to a ship&#39;s hull, causing the ship to sink. &lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;Torpidos&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;Arfogwyd HMS Caroline hefyd gan dorpidos. Roedd torpidos yn ffrwydron tanfor. Maen nhw&#8217;n cael eu lansio mas o diwbiau torpido ac yn symud trwy&#8217;r d&#373;r. Drwy taro&#8217;u targed o dan arwyneb y d&#373;r, roedd torpidos yn gallu achosi difrod niweidiol tu hwnt i gorff llong gan achosi i&#8217;r llong suddo." align="0" color="0x000000" bordercolor="0x484848" borderalpha="1" backgroundcolor="0xffffff" backgroundalpha="1" backgroundvisible="1" borderwidth="1" borderradius="19" wordwrap="1" scrollbar="0" autosize="1" >
